  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/43b11341ca9c267df99c8e9ca9726ae6.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Doomies (Damikira)</i> is a frenetic arcade shooter filled with guns, violence, dark humor, and even a grappling hook!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/86d8b2cf5d8d1255a13997a210a8337e.poster.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/86d8b2cf5d8d1255a13997a210a8337e.webm?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/86d8b2cf5d8d1255a13997a210a8337e.mp4?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s built to help you waste time (in the best way possible) and throw you into a flow state where your only goal is to obliterate freaky enemies and climb the online leaderboard, proving just how much you enjoy staying indoors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It might look simple, but this beast hides layers of chaos under the hood. Beneath the blood and bullets lie secrets, tricks, and twisted mechanics for those brave (or bored) enough to dig deep. Got nothing better to do? Doomies does.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/8d0f7b700a297def61b6a927f86d4759.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔫 <strong>Unlock a wild arsenal of guns</strong> — each louder, nastier, and deadlier than the last</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/9952837e4b4ec58af0942210e7599f04.poster.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/9952837e4b4ec58af0942210e7599f04.webm?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/9952837e4b4ec58af0942210e7599f04.mp4?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😈 <strong>Play as a cast of deranged freaks</strong> — each with unique animations and bad attitudes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎙️ <strong>Fully voiced characters</strong> — because grunting isn’t enough to express this chaos</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📈 <strong>Online leaderboards</strong> — dominate the global rankings or die trying</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🩸 <strong>A freak-ton of blood</strong> — paint the screen red, every time, all the time</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Loud, punchy gunfire</strong> — every shot hits like a drum solo to the face</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Fast, satisfying gameplay</strong> — designed to keep you locked in and fired up</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎸 <strong>Face-melting metal soundtrack</strong> — riffs harder than your uncle’s garage band ever could</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔁 <strong>Slightly randomized levels</strong> — no two runs are the same… or safe</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/027266cd9f4026f77a5d7dd0ceaa61d9.poster.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/027266cd9f4026f77a5d7dd0ceaa61d9.webm?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/027266cd9f4026f77a5d7dd0ceaa61d9.mp4?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤘 <strong>And a hell of a lot of fun, goddammit</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/43b11341ca9c267df99c8e9ca9726ae6.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Doomies (Damikira)</i> is a frenetic arcade shooter filled with guns, violence, dark humor, and even a grappling hook!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/86d8b2cf5d8d1255a13997a210a8337e.poster.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/86d8b2cf5d8d1255a13997a210a8337e.webm?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/86d8b2cf5d8d1255a13997a210a8337e.mp4?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s built to help you waste time (in the best way possible) and throw you into a flow state where your only goal is to obliterate freaky enemies and climb the online leaderboard, proving just how much you enjoy staying indoors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It might look simple, but this beast hides layers of chaos under the hood. Beneath the blood and bullets lie secrets, tricks, and twisted mechanics for those brave (or bored) enough to dig deep. Got nothing better to do? Doomies does.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/8d0f7b700a297def61b6a927f86d4759.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔫 <strong>Unlock a wild arsenal of guns</strong> — each louder, nastier, and deadlier than the last</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/9952837e4b4ec58af0942210e7599f04.poster.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/9952837e4b4ec58af0942210e7599f04.webm?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/9952837e4b4ec58af0942210e7599f04.mp4?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😈 <strong>Play as a cast of deranged freaks</strong> — each with unique animations and bad attitudes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎙️ <strong>Fully voiced characters</strong> — because grunting isn’t enough to express this chaos</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📈 <strong>Online leaderboards</strong> — dominate the global rankings or die trying</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🩸 <strong>A freak-ton of blood</strong> — paint the screen red, every time, all the time</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Loud, punchy gunfire</strong> — every shot hits like a drum solo to the face</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Fast, satisfying gameplay</strong> — designed to keep you locked in and fired up</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎸 <strong>Face-melting metal soundtrack</strong> — riffs harder than your uncle’s garage band ever could</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔁 <strong>Slightly randomized levels</strong> — no two runs are the same… or safe</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/027266cd9f4026f77a5d7dd0ceaa61d9.poster.avif?t=1771877423\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/027266cd9f4026f77a5d7dd0ceaa61d9.webm?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446700/extras/027266cd9f4026f77a5d7dd0ceaa61d9.mp4?t=1771877423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤘 <strong>And a hell of a lot of fun, goddammit</strong></p>",
